channel.title: Riot Shield {ChopStickz} {WireFrame Added}
channel.description:
Here's What i Made, i dunno how long it took wasnt lookin at the time lolol... i just made this for fun... i know it realy has nuttin to do for the days in rs like in the history days lol but i like it :P the one who has it first is the creator of it! now it will exist in the history days :P muahahaha!
Here's some pics of it. btw the "P O L I C E" sign isnt so good but in the game it shows very good, so no need to worry about that.
[IMG]http://i85.photobucket.com/albums/k65/ryanrs2006/RiotShieldWield.jpg[/img]
[IMG]http://i85.photobucket.com/albums/k65/ryanrs2006/RiotShieldWield2.jpg[/img]<-------As u can see here theres the handle for the arm :P i made myself. :)
[IMG]http://i85.photobucket.com/albums/k65/ryanrs2006/RiotShieldWield3.jpg[/img]
WIREFRAME: [IMG]http://i85.photobucket.com/albums/k65/ryanrs2006/WireframeRiotShield.jpg[/img]
EDIT: Since I Made This (Im The First To Post/Make This On MoparScape Forums.) A Bunch Of Other Ppl Where Making It LOL Oh Well.. I Just Want Credits For The Idea Please.
Hope u like, Rate 1/10 plox :P
